description.displayText:
Hello Reviewers Everything was okay the first day the second day it was going good too She offered to go to the store and get things I needed to organize clothes but instead she got decorations for my restroom then said that I owed her 30 extra for paying out of pocket I didn't see a Receipt I didn't ask for it because I trusted so me being so kind I sent her 30 after that I went to run an errand came back she was gone no text no phone call all of my clothes were folded on the dining table I did not see nothing to organize my clothes nothing hanging I just thought she had the things with her but the next day she didn't show other days no show 
Today I got a text saying I owe her $60
